    "This framework can be instantiated in different ways (e.g., there might be several ways of establishing whether A has a sufficiently complete representation of P).",
    "One implementation would be AUP 1: AUP 1 (i-iii) can be measured, given a certain context (series of prompts) via what-, why, and w-questions respectively.",
